OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWet and
OL,6,Fwindy across Northern Ireland and much
OL,7,Fof Scotland overnight, which will
OL,8,Fspread into parts of Wales and western
OL,9,FEngland later. Some clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping elsewhere but with brisk
OL,11,Fwinds it will be a mild night for most.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FRain across the west will
OL,14,Fspread slowly eastwards and weaken
OL,15,Fthroughout the day. Either side there
OL,16,Fwill be some good spells of sunshine,
OL,17,Falthough showers will move into
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland.
